  "reading": "<p><strong>❌ Common misconception:</strong> \\( (a^m)^n = a^{m+n} \\) (add the indices)</p><p><strong>✅ The correct idea:</strong> Power of a power MULTIPLIES the indices. A weak answer adds; a strong answer writes \\( (a^m)^n = a^{mn} \\).</p>",
